& lt ; sharon steel corp > extend exchang offer sharon steel corp said it extend from march six to march 31 the expir date for it debt exchang offer to allow time to complet the sale of it mueller brass co unit and to meet other condit of the offer . the exchang offer cover sharon 's outstand 13.5 pct subordin sink fund debentur due 2000 and it 14.25 pct subordin sink fund debentur due 1990. sharon said that as of march six , 31.6 pct of the 13.5 pct note and 20.9 pct of the 14.25 pct note were tender . the mueller sale is condit on receipt of 80 pct of the note .